main_body:
Task
The group's task shall be the following:
1. to address issues that determine and will determine in the future the competitiveness of the Community agro-food industry and related challenges;
2. to identify the factors that influence the competitive position and sustainability of the Community agro-food industry, including future challenges and trends with an impact on competitiveness;
3. to formulate a set of sector-specific recommendations addressed to policy makers at the Community level.
